svg.title: SOSCredit
svg.desc: Established in 2015, SOS CREDIT is lead by an international team with experience across the finance, payments and marketing industries. The company provides consumer loans issued in Ukraine. Each month SOS CREDIT issues more than 14 thousand loans. The company is able to issue such a high volume because of their machine-learning scoring algorithms, which allows it to check the creditworthiness of a borrower in 5.15 seconds, with manual verifications taking less than 20 minutes.
